## How to develop

```bash
# Bootstrap (one-time, on a fresh clone)
claude-code-meta:init-project

# Daily workflow — dispatch skill auto-routes your prompt
# L0 → codegraph-first lookup, answer in ≤ 1 paragraph
# L1/L2 → tdd-guide → implement → verification-before-completion
# L3 → writing-plans → executing-plans → tdd-guide → verify
# L4 → brainstorming → writing-plans → executing-plans → tdd-guide → code-review

# Weekly self-evolve
claude-code-meta:self-evolve
```

## Versioning

- **Semver**: `vMAJOR.MINOR.PATCH`
- **MAJOR**: breaking API/contract changes
- **MINOR**: backward-compatible features
- **PATCH**: bug fixes, wording

